This paper deals with the problem of reinforcement learning under safety requirements, which is a common topic in the field of machine learning. The paper proposes an algorithm that enables the learning of safety constraints in parallel with reinforcement learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
